4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge, aiming to develop skills in protecting digital environments. The program spans 16 weeks with three live online classes each week, accommodating up to 16 participants per class. Participants will learn to manage Windows, Linux, and server administrations, along with cloud security and penetration testing. The bootcamp emphasizes risk management and compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. At completion, students receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. The curriculum is available in both English and Spanish. For more details, visit: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop